customer relationship, or better integrate with Meta ads.

It=E2=80=99s not without cost, of course: Buy with Prime entails keeping in=
ventory at Amazon fulfillment centers, which means a storage fee, and then =
for every order there is a fulfillment fee (based on size), a prime service=
 fee (3% of the order value), and a payment processing fee (2.4% + $0.30 =
=E2=80=94 more on this in a moment). The fees are almost certainly worth it=
