N1A4tOmMWdajdzzqOv2w8CyA ) , and management wasn=E2=80=99t completely dismi=
ssive about making a deal for Amazon. To me it seemed like a clear opportun=
ity for a deal ( https://stratechery.com/2023/shopify-exits-logistics-the-s=
hopify-logistics-side-quest-whither-buy-with-prime/?access_token=3DeyJhbGci=
